    "Ablation studies verify the contribution of bidirectional C2F enhancement to the localization and recognition of small objects.",
    "The C2F block is an effective architectural innovation for multi-scale visual modeling.",
    "The YOLOv8 model efficiently utilizes the characteristics found in the layers of the CNN by making these adjustments.",
    "This careful balance of deep and shallow feature extraction allows the model to accurately identify and locate diminutive and feeble entities within images while minimizing the computational burden.",
